					"type": 23,
					"value": "To trigger in Multiplayer or following these repro steps.\r\nREPRO STEPS:\r\n1. Start the game.\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. goto -453.75, 27.06, -541.25\r\n4. Move to the other raft.\r\n5. Talk to Duergar Scout standing on top floor (-452.92, 30.51, -525.28)"
